x_938076_now_utils_now_utils_fix_scripts.description: In Madrid, a new software_model_result column has been added to software_model_result. We will upgrade only the latest product results so that the new License Workbench will work with the customer's latest recon results. Though the License Workbench is available in samp, this new field has been added in sams like other recon result fields. So the upgrade script will also live in sams.
